Introduction

ICHILLIN' is a seven-member girl group under KM Entertainment. They officially debuted on September 8, 2021, with the digital single "Got'ya".

The group's name, ICHILLIN', is a combination of the words "Aisling" and "Chillin'". Their official motto is: If you're Chillin, I'm Chillin. Hello, we are ICHILLIN'!

On July 15, 2022, KM Entertainment announced Sohee would leave the group after discussing her future with the company. On October 25, 2022, KM Entertainment announced that Jeong Jiyoon from Girls Planet 999 would join the group for their next comeback Draw (MY TIME).
